{
  "stem": "58.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Every machine got up in 10, 12 feet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had to put them up straight, take them down.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was no work like today.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had to roll them on tubes, for miles.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We pushed them, and then you took from the front the tube, from the back the tube, and put in the front again, and that's how-- and we worked there for months.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then they-- they-- the Allies bombed the-- the factories that made ball bearings, because this was for-- for the war, for planes, for tanks.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I think it was Schweinfurt, if I'm not mistaken.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They bombed all the-- so they brought in the machinery to the salt mine.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They put me to work to make the little balls.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There was one machine that cut precisely, and the other one made it round.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It's like-- there was a machine that round it up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Then it went to another place that put it in the ball bearings.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They put it in grease and put it in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There were women sitting-- Ukrainian women.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that's how I worked for a while.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And one day, the-- when I came in-- we came in from Poland, we all looked good, because you were, like, almost at home.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You helped yourself.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "In [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Czechow, ?] I used to work for the factory that made the material.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We used to get some Polish soup that they serve to their own.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we came in really not-- not skinny, you know, like we became after.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The boss comes over to me and says, Liber, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Every day-- I'm going to say it in English-- every day you're getting skinnier.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was afraid to say something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, in those days I were so nervous.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
